name: SzETROOM - DIAMETER
description:
This work are participated on Yogyakarta Komik Weeks "DIPENDAM PANDEMI", October 9-15th 2020 at Sonobudoyo (Ex-KONI Building) Central Java - Indonesia. But never collected by anyone or uploaded anywhere by me.

The lyrics are a National Indonesian Language (Bahasa) that describing a condition from quarantine days (in a SzETROOM way), sang by SzETROOM vocalist: Alienpang and her friend Apleer Jajaa backing up as a fly sound.

Concept / Illustration / Animation / Music Arranger / Bass / Guitar / Drum Machine / Composer / Lyricist / Recorded / Mixed / Mastered by Yours Truly: Bronzelani / zE at zEtudio.
